class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/igorrybalko\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/18c096ea723771ae0ecd4d980e67e82a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/18c096ea723771ae0ecd4d980e67e82a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/igorrybalko\" class=\"reviewer-name\">igorrybalko</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 26, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">As for free</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Pretty Good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tony014\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bf1fbe65109ae1501ec216da25904c5f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bf1fbe65109ae1501ec216da25904c5f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tony014\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Tony Brauer <small>(tony014)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 25, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I manage a yacht club site and WooCommerce plugins have provided the means by which we can  API link with Xero for membership invoices and sync our MailChimp distribution list.  This provides a huge saving of time for the volunteers who manage the club in their own time.\n\nHowever, I found it a bit clunky, as I\'m one of those club volunteers and a relatively inexperienced WordPress web developer.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Removed Product Management and All Products!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/julieanime\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/abc93a04abb268680db7e943226dc9cf?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/abc93a04abb268680db7e943226dc9cf?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/julieanime\" class=\"reviewer-name\">\'Girl on The Bus\' <small>(julieanime)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 24, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thankfully, the websites not live yet.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Makes Wordpress a viable E-Commerce Platform</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nicksamuel\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b8ae5f207a0dc0e5518184aaada82d09?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b8ae5f207a0dc0e5518184aaada82d09?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nicksamuel\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Nick Samuel <small>(nicksamuel)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 24, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve been involved in several Woo-Commerce builds and have worked on the SEO for several existing sites. \n\nWoo-Commerce/Wordpress is a dream to use and very SEO friendly out of the box.\n\nClients we migrated it to found it easy to use (compared to Magento), and pretty much any functionality they had previously or need already exists as a Woo-Commerce extension. \n\nPlus the range of extensions both free and premium is growing with each passing month!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">So Good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gang618\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/74fca434a359aad90663836411ef688c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/74fca434a359aad90663836411ef688c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gang618\" class=\"reviewer-name\">gang618</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 24, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">So Good Yet Easy To Use.\n\nThanks.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.3.6.2.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:6:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=2074177\";s:7:\"caption\";b:0;}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=2074177\";s:7:\"caption\";b:0;}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=2074177\";s:7:\"caption\";b:0;}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-4.jpg?rev=2074177\";s:7:\"caption\";b:0;}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-5.jpg?rev=2074177\";s:7:\"caption\";b:0;}i:6;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-6.jpg?rev=2074177\";s:7:\"caption\";b:0;}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:10:\"e-commerce\";s:10:\"e-commerce\";s:9:\"ecommerce\";s:9:\"ecommerce\";s:5:\"sales\";s:5:\"sales\";s:4:\"sell\";s:4:\"sell\";s:5:\"store\";s:5:\"store\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:57:{s:5:\"3.0.0\";s:60:\"https://download